      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just because i've been drinking like nothing but coffee and energy drinks all week... and i definitely havent slept much. i mean, it's mostly just a dull ache now, not that lightning thing anymore. u think i could just wait it out with some ibuprofen and a big bottle of water? i really don't want to go to the clinic if i don't have to, it's like 3am here.",
